---
title: Nan's Chicken & Roast Veggie Traybake with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Our popular Nan's special seasoning - a perfect blend of paprika, pepper, onion and garlic - instantly adds a rich,
traditional flavour to succulent chicken breast. Add a creamy pesto dressing and roasted veggies for a dish worth
enjoying again and again.

